02:25:23,270 --> 02:25:25,030
你连自己都迷失了
You're not yourself.

1929
02:25:25,910 --> 02:25:28,030
我认识的梭林会毫不犹豫进去的...
The Thorin I know would not hesitate to go in there...

1930
02:25:28,310 --> 02:25:28,870
我不会...
I will not risk...

1931
02:25:29,110 --> 02:25:32,910
为救一个飞贼而冒险的
this quest for the life of one burglar.

1932
02:25:34,790 --> 02:25:36,230
他有名字
Bilbo.

1933
02:25:36,590 --> 02:25:38,510
叫比尔博
His name is Bilbo.

1934
02:25:42,270 --> 02:25:44,070
是橡木盾...
It's Oakenshield...

1935
02:25:44,350 --> 02:25:47,320
那个可恶的矮人篡位者
that filthy Dwarvish usurper.

1936
02:25:49,550 --> 02:25:51,710
是他派你...
He sent you in here...

1937
02:25:51,950 --> 02:25:54,710
来拿阿肯宝石 对吧?
for the Arkenstone, didn't he?

1938
02:25:54,950 --> 02:25:55,590
不 不...
No. No...

1939
02:25:55,830 --> 02:25:58,720
不 我不知道你在说什么
no. I don't know what you're talking about.

1940
02:25:58,950 --> 02:26:00,070
不用否认了
Don't bother denying it.

1941
02:26:01,470 --> 02:26:03,270
我早就猜到了他的阴谋诡计
I guessed his foul purpose some time ago.

1942
02:26:05,870 --> 02:26:07,470
但没关系
But it matters not.

1943
02:26:08,630 --> 02:26:10,990
橡木盾的计划不会得逞
Oakenshield's quest will fail.

1944
02:26:12,990 --> 02:26:14,750
黑暗即将来临
The darkness is coming.

1945
02:26:15,590 --> 02:26:19,590
淹没世界的每一个角落
It will spread to every corner of the land.

1946
02:27:02,190 --> 02:27:05,350
躲在阴影里的小偷 你被利用了
You are being used, thief in the shadows.

1947
02:27:05,790 --> 02:27:09,350
你永远只是达到目的的手段而已
You were only ever a means to an end.

1948
02:27:10,190 --> 02:27:13,600
胆小的橡木盾衡量过...
The coward Oakenshield has weighed...

1949
02:27:13,870 --> 02:27:15,440
你的生命价值了...
the value of your life...

1950
02:27:15,710 --> 02:27:17,870
你一文不值
and found it worth nothing.

1951
02:27:18,470 --> 02:27:19,670
不
No.

1952
02:27:20,390 --> 02:27:21,390
不
No.

1953
02:27:22,350 --> 02:27:23,350
不 你在说谎
No, you're lying.

1954
02:27:23,590 --> 02:27:24,750
他向你承诺什么了?
What did he promise you?

1955
02:27:25,190 --> 02:27:27,270
分你一份宝藏吗?
A share of the treasure?

1956
02:27:28,270 --> 02:27:29,430
说得好像宝藏...
As if it was his...

1957
02:27:29,670 --> 02:27:30,750
是他的一样
to give.

1958
02:27:31,590 --> 02:27:33,350
我不会放弃...
I will not part with...

1959
02:27:33,590 --> 02:27:34,590
一个子儿
a single coin.

1960
02:27:35,270 --> 02:27:37,790
一个都不会放弃
Not one piece of it.

1961
02:27:41,670 --> 02:27:42,670
我的牙齿...
My teeth...

1962
02:27:42,790 --> 02:27:43,990
尖如利剑
are swords.

1963
02:27:44,870 --> 02:27:48,190
我的爪子利如长矛
My claws are spears.

1964
02:27:50,310 --> 02:27:51,470
我的双翼...
My wings...

1965
02:27:52,110 --> 02:27:54,630
强如暴风
are a hurricane.

1966
02:28:00,270 --> 02:28:02,110
传说是真的
So it is true.

1967
02:28:02,470 --> 02:28:04,630
黑箭确实命中了目标
The Black Arrow found its mark.

1968
02:28:04,870 --> 02:28:05,870
你说什么?
What did you say?

1969
02:28:06,630 --> 02:28:10,520
我只是说我久闻您的大名...
I was just saying your reputation precedes you, O Smaug...

1970
02:28:10,750 --> 02:28:11,950
噢 君主史矛革
the Tyrannical.

1971
02:28:12,550 --> 02:28:13,630
您确实
Truly.

1972
02:28:13,870 --> 02:28:15,830
是世上无人能及的
You have no equal on this earth.

1973
02:28:20,270 --> 02:28:24,430
为了看到橡木盾痛苦...
I am almost tempted to let you take it...

1974
02:28:24,870 --> 02:28:26,870
我差点让你...
if only to see Oakenshield...

1975
02:28:27,150 --> 02:28:28,150
拿到宝石了
suffer.

1976
02:28:29,190 --> 02:28:30,270
这样就能...
Watch it...

1977
02:28:30,510 --> 02:28:32,030
看着宝石毁灭他
destroy him.

1978
02:28:32,510 --> 02:28:35,630
吞噬他的心灵...
Watch it corrupt his heart...

1979
02:28:36,310 --> 02:28:38,710
让他发狂
and drive him mad.

1980
02:28:41,910 --> 02:28:43,480
但我想还是不要了
But I think not.

1981
02:28:44,070 --> 02:28:46,310
小游戏到此结束吧
I think our little game ends here.

1982
02:28:47,150 --> 02:28:48,390
告诉我...
So tell me...

1983
02:28:48,670 --> 02:28:49,670
小偷...
thief...

1984
02:28:50,430 --> 02:28:52,550
你想怎样死?
how do you choose to die?

1985
02:29:35,990 --> 02:29:36,990
不是
Nah.

1986
02:30:05,190 --> 02:30:07,230
爸? 是你吗 爸?
Da? Is that you, Da?

1987
02:30:40,350 --> 02:30:41,680
- 啊!  - 躲下去!
- Aah!  - Stay down!

1988
02:31:42,510 --> 02:31:43,510
趴下!
Get down!

1989
02:32:19,710 --> 02:32:20,870
你把他们都杀了
You killed them all.

1990
02:32:21,110 --> 02:32:22,190
还有其他的
There are others.

1991
02:32:22,630 --> 02:32:23,710
陶瑞尔
Tauriel.

1992
02:32:24,190 --> 02:32:25,310
我们走
Come.

1993
02:32:29,350 --> 02:32:30,350
他快死了
We're losing him.

1994
02:32:34,230 --> 02:32:35,430
陶瑞尔
Tauriel.

1995
02:33:05,630 --> 02:33:06,710
你要做什么?
What are you doing?

1996
02:33:09,710 --> 02:33:11,430
我要救他
I'm going to save him.

1997
02:33:32,190 --> 02:33:33,670
- 你还活着!  - 活不了多久了!
- You're alive!  - Not for much longer.

1998
02:33:33,750 --> 02:33:36,720
- 你找到阿肯宝石了吗? 阿肯宝石  - 龙追来了
- Did you find the Arkenstone? The Arkenstone.  - The dragon's coming.

1999
02:33:39,670 --> 02:33:41,240
你找到了吗?
Did you find it?

2000
02:33:46,750 --> 02:33:47,830
我们要赶紧离开
We have to get out.

2001
02:33:51,550 --> 02:33:52,550
梭林
Thorin.

2002
02:33:56,270 --> 02:33:57,390
梭林
Thorin.

2003
02:34:27,830 --> 02:34:29,950
我要烧死你们!
You will burn!

2004
02:34:31,110 --> 02:34:32,110
- 跑!  - 啊!
- Run!  - Ah!

2005
02:34:39,110 --> 02:34:40,190
快点 比尔博!
Come on, Bilbo!

2006
02:34:53,070 --> 02:34:54,110
快走
Come on.

2007
02:35:11,270 --> 02:35:12,470
压住他
Hold him down.

2008
02:35:28,870 --> 02:35:30,590
呃! 蒂尔达
Unh! Tilda.

2009
02:36:23,470 --> 02:36:24,670
嘘 小声点!
Shh, Shh, Shh!

2010
02:36:32,510 --> 02:36:33,950
我们甩开它了
We've given him the slip.

2011
02:36:34,190 --> 02:36:35,190
不
No.

2012
02:36:35,670 --> 02:36:37,870
它可狡猾了
He's too cunning for that.

2013
02:36:39,630 --> 02:36:40,750
那现在去哪儿?
So where to now?

2014
02:36:41,350 --> 02:36:42,680
西边的警卫室
The western guardroom.

2015
02:36:43,390 --> 02:36:44,910
可能有路可逃
There may be a way out.

2016
02:36:45,190 --> 02:36:47,190
那里太高了 没可能...
It's too high. There's no chance...

2017
02:36:47,430 --> 02:36:49,510
- 逃出去  - 那是我们唯一的机会
- that way.  - it's our only chance.

2018
02:36:50,830 --> 02:36:52,320
我们只能放手一搏
We have to try.

2019
02:37:08,870 --> 02:37:10,030
来
Come on.

2020
02:37:57,550 --> 02:38:01,310
我听过精灵神药的传说
I've heard tell of the wonders of Elvish medicine.

2021
02:38:01,550 --> 02:38:04,280
今天有幸亲眼看到了
That was a privilege to witness.

2022
02:38:06,750 --> 02:38:07,910
陶瑞尔
Tauriel.

2023
02:38:12,230 --> 02:38:13,430
躺着别动
Lie still.

2024
02:38:20,630 --> 02:38:22,750
你不可能是她
You cannot be her.

2025
02:38:26,230 --> 02:38:28,390
她在遥远的地方
She is far away.

2026
02:38:32,590 --> 02:38:34,000
她离我...
She is far...

2027
02:38:34,230 --> 02:38:35,830
很远很远
far away from me.

2028
02:38:37,470 --> 02:38:39,590
她行走在...
She walks...

2029
02:38:39,830 --> 02:38:42,510
另一个世界的星光之下
in starlight in another world.

2030
02:38:47,830 --> 02:38:49,790
只是个梦而已
It was just a dream.

2031
02:39:01,470 --> 02:39:03,710
你觉得她爱过我吗?
Do you think she could've loved me?

2032
02:39:11,030 --> 02:39:12,030
跟紧一点
Stay close.

2033
02:39:22,430 --> 02:39:23,430
到尽头了
That's it, then.

2034
02:39:24,470 --> 02:39:26,310
无路可走
There's no way out.

2035
02:39:32,710 --> 02:39:34,950
我们同胞的尸骨
The last of our kin.

2036
02:39:38,630 --> 02:39:40,710
他们肯定带着...
They must have come here...

2037
02:39:41,390 --> 02:39:42,430
巨大的希望...
hoping...

2038
02:39:42,670 --> 02:39:43,830
来到这里
beyond hope.

2039
02:39:53,590 --> 02:39:55,910
我们可以下到金矿里
We could try to reach the mines.

2040
02:39:56,750 --> 02:39:58,990
也许能撑上几天
We might last a few days.

2041
02:40:01,150 --> 02:40:02,190
不
No.

2042
02:40:05,150 --> 02:40:07,390
我不会这样死去的
I will not die like this.

2043
02:40:08,750 --> 02:40:09,910
蜷缩着
Cowering.

2044
02:40:10,790 --> 02:40:12,590
挣扎着 奄奄一息
Clawing for breath.

2045
02:40:17,510 --> 02:40:18,630
我们引它去熔炉
We make for the forges.

2046
02:40:18,910 --> 02:40:20,870
它会看到我们的 必死无疑
He'll see us, sure as death.

2047
02:40:21,110 --> 02:40:22,350
如果我们分头行事就不会
Not if we split up.

2048
02:40:22,590 --> 02:40:23,590
梭林...
Thorin...

2049
02:40:23,830 --> 02:40:25,320
我们绝对逃不掉了
we'll never make it.

2050
02:40:25,550 --> 02:40:27,070
也许有人能逃掉
Some of us might.

2051
02:40:27,470 --> 02:40:29,710
引它去熔炉
Lead him to the forges.

2052
02:40:30,470 --> 02:40:32,470
我们要杀掉恶龙
We kill the dragon.

2053
02:40:34,190 --> 02:40:36,470
若一切注定焚尽...
If this is to end in fire...

2054
02:40:36,910 --> 02:40:39,310
那我们也将同赴火海
then we will all burn together.

2055
02:40:40,630 --> 02:40:41,790
这边
This way.

2056
02:40:46,270 --> 02:40:47,270
逃吧
Flee.

2057
02:40:47,950 --> 02:40:48,950
逃吧
Flee.

2058
02:40:49,870 --> 02:40:51,830
逃命吧
Run for your lives.

2059
02:40:52,590 --> 02:40:53,590
你们...
There is...

2060
02:40:54,110 --> 02:40:56,310
无处可藏了
nowhere to hide.

2061
02:40:56,550 --> 02:40:57,550
看你背后!
Behind you!

2062
02:40:57,750 --> 02:40:58,750
小虫子!
Worm!

2063
02:40:59,750 --> 02:41:00,750
来!
Come on!

2064
02:41:02,790 --> 02:41:03,830
快跑!
Run!

2065
02:41:05,790 --> 02:41:07,070
嘿 你!
Hey, you!

2066
02:41:07,430 --> 02:41:08,430
这里!
Here!

2067
02:44:06,150 --> 02:44:08,110
这边 是这边!
This way. It's this way!

2068
02:44:08,390 --> 02:44:09,510
来!
Come on!

2069
02:44:09,750 --> 02:44:10,750
梭林!
Thorin!

2070
02:44:16,110 --> 02:44:17,230
跟着巴林!
Follow Balin!

2071
02:44:18,430 --> 02:44:19,670
- 梭林!  - 快!
- Thorin.  - Come on!

2072
02:44:35,510 --> 02:44:36,870
梭林!
Thorin!

2073
02:44:45,950 --> 02:44:46,990
接着!
Hold on!

2074
02:45:20,830 --> 02:45:22,160
梭林!
Thorin!

2075
02:45:25,030 --> 02:45:26,600
走 走!
Go. Go!

2076
02:45:30,310 --> 02:45:33,990
这个计划行不通 这些熔炉是冰冷的
The plan's not gonna work. These furnaces are stone cold.

2077
02:45:34,230 --> 02:45:35,590
他说得对 我们...
He's right. We've no...

2078
02:45:35,830 --> 02:45:38,150
没有火能点着熔炉
fire hot enough to set them ablaze.

2079
02:45:40,710 --> 02:45:42,070
我们没有吗?
Have we not?

2080
02:45:43,630 --> 02:45:46,550
我不觉得你会那么容易以智取胜
I did not look to see you so easily outwitted.

2081
02:45:50,510 --> 02:45:51,150
你已经变得...
You have grown...

2082
02:45:51,390 --> 02:45:53,350
又慢又肥...
slow and fat...

2083
02:45:54,190 --> 02:45:55,190
你这臃肿的...
in your dotage...

2084
02:45:57,510 --> 02:45:58,670
老糊涂!
slug!

2085
02:46:00,070 --> 02:46:01,750
躲起来 快!
Take cover. Go!

2086
02:46:29,190 --> 02:46:29,870
邦伯!
Bombur!

2087
02:46:30,190 --> 02:46:31,600
让火烧得更猛些
Get those bellows working.

2088
02:46:31,830 --> 02:46:32,950
快!
Go!

2089
02:46:46,750 --> 02:46:47,310
比尔博!
Bilbo!

2090
02:46:47,590 --> 02:46:49,310
上去那儿 听我指令...
Up there. On my mark...

2091
02:46:49,590 --> 02:46:50,870
拉那条杠
pull that lever.

2092
02:47:01,390 --> 02:47:03,710
巴林! 你还能配制出闪火吗?
Balin! Can you still mix a flash-flame?

2093
02:47:03,950 --> 02:47:06,350
可以 只需要一会儿 来!
Aye. It'll only take a jiffy. Come on!

2094
02:47:08,110 --> 02:47:09,550
我们没有时间了
We don't have a jiffy.

2095
02:47:21,510 --> 02:47:22,630
硫磺在哪儿?
Where's the sulfur?

2096
02:47:23,030 --> 02:47:24,030
你知道自己...
You sure you know what...

2097
02:47:24,110 --> 02:47:25,110
在做什么吗?
you're doing?

2098
02:47:36,550 --> 02:47:37,550
快点!
Come on!

2099
02:47:59,630 --> 02:48:00,630
拉杠!
Now!

2100
02:49:57,070 --> 02:49:59,150
引它去众王之廊
Lead him to the Gallery of the Kings.

2101
02:50:47,230 --> 02:50:48,230
不要停下来 比尔博!
Keep going, Bilbo!

2102
02:50:48,790 --> 02:50:49,870
跑!
Run!

2103
02:51:35,190 --> 02:51:39,190
你以为能骗得了我吗 骑桶者?
You think you can deceive me, Barrel-rider?

2104
02:51:41,950 --> 02:51:44,950
你来自长湖镇
You have come from Lake-town.

2105
02:51:46,670 --> 02:51:47,950
这是...
This is some...

2106
02:51:48,190 --> 02:51:51,470
可恶的矮人和悲惨的长湖人...
sordid scheme hatched between these filthy Dwarves...

2107
02:51:51,710 --> 02:51:54,870
策划的阴谋
and those miserable tub-trading Lakemen.

2108
02:51:55,870 --> 02:51:57,790
那些带着...
Those sniveling cowards...

2109
02:51:58,030 --> 02:51:59,520
长弓和黑箭...
with their long bows...

2110
02:51:59,750 --> 02:52:02,590
哭哭啼啼的胆小鬼
and Black Arrows.

2111
02:52:02,950 --> 02:52:04,830
也许我该...
Perhaps it is time...

2112
02:52:05,110 --> 02:52:06,990
拜访一下他们
I paid them a visit.

2113
02:52:07,510 --> 02:52:08,750
不
Oh, no.

2114
02:52:10,630 --> 02:52:12,120
这不是他们的错!
This isn't their fault!

2115
02:52:12,350 --> 02:52:13,350
等等!
Wait!

2116
02:52:13,390 --> 02:52:14,990
你不能去长湖镇!
You cannot go to Lake-town!

2117
02:52:16,910 --> 02:52:19,070
你在乎他们...
You care about them...

2118
02:52:19,790 --> 02:52:21,030
对吧?
Do you?

2119
02:52:21,270 --> 02:52:22,270
那就好
Good.

2120
02:52:22,950 --> 02:52:25,360
你可以看着他们死去
Then you can watch them die.

2121
02:52:30,910 --> 02:52:32,030
这里!
Here!

2122
02:52:32,950 --> 02:52:33,950
你这个无知的废物
You witless worm.

2123
02:52:40,790 --> 02:52:42,200
是你
You.

2124
02:52:42,590 --> 02:52:45,070
我要拿回你偷的东西
I am taking back what you stole.

2125
02:52:49,110 --> 02:52:49,750
你...
You...

2126
02:52:50,030 --> 02:52:51,600
什么也...
will take nothing...

2127
02:52:51,870 --> 02:52:53,520
拿不回去...
from me...

2128
02:52:53,790 --> 02:52:54,950
矮人
Dwarf.

2129
02:52:55,430 --> 02:52:58,710
我打败了你们老一辈的...
I laid low your warriors...

2130
02:52:58,950 --> 02:53:00,550
战士
of old.

2131
02:53:00,830 --> 02:53:03,190
在人类心中...
I instilled terror in...

2132
02:53:03,430 --> 02:53:05,110
植入恐惧
the hearts of Men.

2133
02:53:06,270 --> 02:53:07,710
我才是...
I am...

2134
02:53:07,950 --> 02:53:11,630
山下之王
King Under the Mountain.

2135
02:53:12,070 --> 02:53:14,350
这不是你的王国
This is not your kingdom.

2136
02:53:14,590 --> 02:53:16,590
这是矮人之地
These are Dwarf lands.

2137
02:53:17,350 --> 02:53:18,350
这是矮人之金
This is Dwarf gold.

2138
02:53:20,670 --> 02:53:21,390
我们要...
